#: .\modinfo.json
msgid "Pneumatic fun"
msgstr "气动乐趣"

#. ~ Description for Pneumatic fun
#: .\modinfo.json
msgid "Adds strong craftable pebbles for pneumatic weapons"
msgstr "为气动武器添加可制作的强力鹅卵石"

#: .\Items\Ammo.json .\Items\Ammo_types.json
msgid "modified mininuke"
msgid_plural "modified mininukes"
msgstr[0] "改装微型核弹"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'modified mininuke'}
#: .\Items\Ammo.json
msgid ""
"A heavily modified handheld nuclear device on a rocket.  Intended to be "
"fired from a specialized launcher, it has been rigged to explode on impact "
"instead of on a timer.  It can fly further than the explosion will reach, "
"probably."
msgstr "一枚经过大幅改装的火箭式手持核装置。原本设计用于专用发射器发射，现被改装为撞击引爆而非定时引爆。它的飞行距离可能远超爆炸范围。"

#: .\Items\Ammo.json
msgid "Iron-coated pebble"
msgid_plural "Iron-coated pebbles"
msgstr[0] "铁包覆鹅卵石"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Iron-coated pebble'}
#: .\Items\Ammo.json
msgid ""
"Pebble - Mark II, needs some time and special equipment to create but "
"totally worth it if you want to step up your armor-piercing game with "
"pneumatics"
msgstr "鹅卵石 - Mark II，需要一些时间和特殊设备来制作，但如果你想在气动武器上提升穿甲能力，这完全值得。"

#: .\Items\Ammo.json
msgid "Iron-coated clay pellet"
msgid_plural "Iron-coated clay pellets"
msgstr[0] "铁包覆粘土弹丸"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Iron-coated clay pellet'}
#: .\Items\Ammo.json
msgid ""
"A clay pellet coated with iron - Mark II, needs some time and special "
"equipment to create but totally worth it if you want to step up your armor-"
"piercing game with pneumatics that use pebble ammo."
msgstr "铁包覆的粘土弹丸 - Mark II，需要一些时间和特殊设备来制作，但如果你想在使用鹅卵石弹药的气动武器上提升穿甲能力，这完全值得。"

#: .\Items\Ammo.json
msgid "Bone-coated pebble"
msgid_plural "Bone-coated pebbles"
msgstr[0] "骨包覆鹅卵石"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Bone-coated pebble'}
#: .\Items\Ammo.json
msgid ""
"Pebble - Mark III, you've already seen Skeletal Juggernauts, right?Well this"
" is basically miniature version of it - bone coating infused with blob, for "
"some reason this strange infusion works quite well when you coat the normal "
"pebbles with it"
msgstr ""
"鹅卵石 - Mark "
"III，你已经见过骷髅巨像了吧？嗯，这基本上是它的微型版本——骨涂层中注入了粘液，不知为何，这种奇怪的注入物在涂覆普通鹅卵石时效果相当好。"

#: .\Items\Ammo.json
msgid "Alloy-coated pebble"
msgid_plural "Alloy-coated pebbles"
msgstr[0] "合金包覆鹅卵石"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Alloy-coated pebble'}
#: .\Items\Ammo.json
msgid ""
"Pebble - Mark IV, much deadlier but harder to craft version of 'Pebble - "
"Mark ii', synthesis of rigid alloy and living blob truly makes this ammo "
"spectacular, peculiar even, who would have thought that blob can be turned "
"into living ammo?"
msgstr ""
"鹅卵石 - Mark IV，比'鹅卵石 - Mark "
"II'更致命但更难制作的版本，刚性合金与活体粘液的合成真正使这种弹药变得惊人，甚至奇特，谁能想到粘液可以变成活体弹药？"
